  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective database has two main objectives;

        -  to evaluate the complication rates, 30-day and 90-day mortality from different surgical
           strategies for unresectable, borderline resectable or initially unresectable liver
           metastasis from colorectal cancer.

        -  to establish baseline quality parameters for different surgical strategies for
           unresectable, borderline and initially unresectable colorectal liver metastasis (CRLM)
           patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
